+ "OpenOffice Word"    Exec exec oowriter
+ "openOffice Excel"    Exec exec oocalc
+ "openOffice PowerPoint"    Exec exec ooimpres

DestroyMenu "ToolAppsGraphics"
AddToMenu "ToolAppsGraphics"
